transcript:
Hello, sorry.
Ji sir, Ankush ji.
Ji.
Ankush ji, sir good morning. Mera naam Swapnil Tiwari hai. IndiaMART head office se baat karta tha Noida se.
Ji, ji boliye.
Sir aapne na ek issue raise kiya hua tha account manager ko leke. I think aapki baat hui hogi Raksha Singh jo aapke account ko handle karti hain. To sir kuch problem aa raha tha account manager se?
Sir actually main abhi market mein hoon, baat nahi kar paunga.
Achha, to sir abhi kab call karun aapko?
Aadhe ghante baad kar dijiye.
Thik hai, aadhe ghante mein main connect karta hoon sir. Okay.
